Inpatient cost parameters

Source: R/data.R
params_costs_inpt.Rd

Mean inpatient costs by health state.

params_costs_inpt

Format

A data table with the following columns:

state_name

Name of the health state.

mean

Mean outpatient costs.

se

Standard error of outpatient costs.

ref

BibTeX reference for estimate.

Examples

print(params_costs_inpt)
#>    state_name  mean   se ref
#> 1:         S1 30000 3000  NA
#> 2:      P1/S2 20000 4000  NA
#> 3:         P2 22000 4200  NA
